---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Terms of Use | CareCost Intelligence" description="Read the terms for using CareCost Intelligence tools and content, including acceptable use, intellectual property, limitations of liability, and policy updates.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Terms of Use</h1>
      <p class="note">Updated: Feb 2026. These terms govern your use of this site and its planning tools.</p>
      <div class="tag">Last updated: Feb 2026</div>
      <div class="editorial-meta">Reviewed by CareCost Intelligence Editorial Team</div>
      <div class="author-box">
        <div class="author-title">Editorial review</div>
        <div class="author-meta">
          <div>
            <strong>CareCost Intelligence Editorial Team</strong>
            <p class="note">Planning guidance updated annually. Read our <a href="/editorial-policy/">Editorial Policy</a>, <a href="/data-sources/">Data Sources</a>, or <a href="/contact/">report a correction</a>.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="chip-grid" style="margin-top: 12px;">
        <a class="chip" href="#eligibility">Eligibility</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#planning-only">Planning-only use</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#acceptable-use">Acceptable use</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#intellectual-property">Intellectual property</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#no-guarantees">No guarantees</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#links">External links</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#changes">Changes</a>
        <a class="chip" href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="eligibility">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Eligibility</h2>
      <p>This site is intended for adults planning senior care costs. By using the site, you confirm you are at least 18 years old and able to enter into these terms.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="planning-only">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Planning-only use</h2>
      <p>All tools and guides are provided for planning and comparison. They do not provide medical, legal, or financial advice, and do not replace professional guidance or facility quotes.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Estimates are informational and based on your inputs.</li>
        <li>Facility pricing varies by care needs and local market conditions.</li>
        <li>Use the estimator to compare scenarios, not to finalize decisions.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="acceptable-use">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
      <p>Use the site for personal planning or professional research. Do not use the site in ways that harm the service, users, or data integrity.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Do not attempt to access or disrupt site infrastructure.</li>
        <li>Do not scrape or harvest content at scale without permission.</li>
        <li>Do not misrepresent estimates as official provider quotes.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="intellectual-property">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>All site content, templates, and tools are owned by CareCost Intelligence unless otherwise noted. You may reference guides for personal use, but commercial redistribution requires written permission.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="no-guarantees">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>No guarantees</h2>
      <p>We strive to keep the site accurate and updated, but we do not guarantee accuracy, completeness, or availability. Use the site at your own risk.</p>
      <p class="note">If a tool is unavailable or returns an error, we are not liable for decisions made without verified quotes.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="links">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>Some pages link to third-party resources. We do not control or endorse those sites and are not responsible for their content or privacy practices.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="changes">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these terms as the site evolves. Continued use means you accept the revised terms.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="contact">
    <div class="container card">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@carecostintel.com">hello@carecostintel.com</a>.</p>
      <p class="note">Please do not send sensitive medical information by email.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
